OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784740728
OL,3,CMajor investigation after two trailers
OL,4,Cof waste abandoned on road
OL,6,FA major fly-tipping investigation has
OL,7,Fbeen launched after two trailers
OL,8,Fpacked with waste were abandoned on a
OL,9,FLincolnshire road.
OL,11,FNorth Lincolnshire Council says the
OL,12,Ftrailers were left on Ramsden Road
OL,13,Fnear Flixborough Industrial Estate
OL,14,Fover the weekend, between Saturday 27
OL,15,Fto Monday 29 June.
OL,17,FThe trailers - one of which is missing
OL,18,Fa wheel and neither of which have
OL,19,Flights - appear to have had large
OL,20,Fholes cut into their roofs, allowing
OL,21,Fthem to be filled from above.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784740728
OL,3,CMajor investigation after two trailers
OL,4,Cof waste abandoned on road
OL,6,FThe damage means the doors cannot be
OL,7,Fsafely opened so specialist
OL,8,Fcontractors were brought in to
OL,9,Fdismantle and remove the waste.
OL,11,FThe specialist contractors say they
OL,12,Fhave not found any particularly
OL,13,Fhazardous material so far and they've
OL,14,Fmainly found car parts and tyres.
OL,16,FAndy Fidell, Head of Operations at
OL,17,FNorth Lincolnshire Council, said: "I
OL,18,Fthink it's absolutely terrible. At the
OL,19,Fend of the day there's been two
OL,20,Fvehicles that have been abandoned with
OL,21,Fa whole host of different waste in it.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784740728
OL,3,CMajor investigation after two trailers
OL,4,Cof waste abandoned on road
OL,6,F"It's just criminal activity that has
OL,7,Fbeen left for the taxpayer to pick up."
OL,9,FJames Todd, Street Cleansing Manager
OL,10,Fat North Lincolnshire Council, said:
OL,11,F"It's an extremely complex operation
OL,12,Fbecause of the unknowns we need to
OL,13,Fdeal with.
OL,15,F"When trucks are sealed, we just don't
OL,16,Fknow what people have put in them so
OL,17,Fwe have to prepare for every
OL,18,Feventuality.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784740728
OL,3,CMajor investigation after two trailers
OL,4,Cof waste abandoned on road
OL,6,FCllr Rob Waltham, leader of North
OL,7,FLincolnshire Council, said: "It's
OL,8,Fbreathtakingly irresponsible and
OL,9,Fwhoever has done this should expect us
OL,10,Fto pursue every line of enquiry until
OL,11,Fwe identify them.
OL,13,F"This isn't someone throwing a black
OL,14,Fbag into a hedge. Somebody has
OL,15,Fdeliberately filled two articulated
OL,16,Ftrailers with what appears to be
OL,17,Findustrial waste, hauled them across
OL,18,Four roads and abandoned them without a
OL,19,Fsecond thought for the danger they've
OL,20,Fcreated or the disruption they've
OL,21,Fcaused.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784740728
OL,3,CMajor investigation after two trailers
OL,4,Cof waste abandoned on road
OL,6,F"I'm absolutely determined that those
OL,7,Fresponsible are brought to justice.
OL,8,FFly-tipping on this scale is
OL,9,Fenvironmental crime, plain and simple,
OL,10,Fand we will use every power available
OL,11,Fto us to track down whoever is behind
OL,12,Fit."
OL,14,FRamsden Road is expected to remain
OL,15,Fclosed until 9am on Wednesday 22 July
OL,16,Fwhilst removal works take place.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/5
